lead_paragraph: Greg Chalmers won the Barracuda Championship on Sunday at Montreux for his first PGA Tour title, eagling the final hole for a six-point victory in the modified Stableford scoring event.

headline.print_headline: Greg Chalmers Wins Barracuda for First PGA Tour Title
